item.title: CVE-2021-38174|2024-08-04T01:37:15.770Z -- sap%20se -- sap%203d%20visual%20enterprise%20viewer
item.description: When a user opens manipulated files received from untrusted sources in SAP 3D Visual Enterprise Viewer version - 9, the application crashes and becomes temporarily unavailable to the user until restart of the application.
